      </p>
  </article>
</div>
    <div class="teaser-listing-item">




<article class="teaser teaser-lg blog-entry--teaser" data-nid="5019365">

  <div class="teaser-lg--main">

          <div class="teaser-lg__image">
        
              <a href="/us/blog/intentional-insights/202404/what-is-the-real-impact-of-flexible-work-on-mental-health"><img loading="lazy" src="https://cdn2.psychologytoday.com/assets/styles/manual_crop_1_1_288x288/public/teaser_image/blog_entry/2024-04/laptop-6062423_1280.jpg?itok=0PsQ-ytW" width="288" height="288" alt="" title="Firmbee/Pixabay" />

</a>

      
      </div>
    
